        <mxCell id="seq_text" value="① SDK → AG ONE Gateway (chat / gesture / chip)&#xa;② AG ONE → Experion /process (embed → semantic cache → NLP intent router)&#xa;③ Experion → AG ONE: { intent: ACTION | GENERATION, actionKey?, productContext }&#xa;④ AG ONE Orchestrator → Product Action Handler OR Product Generation Service (per routing table)&#xa;⑤ Product backend executes → returns product-specific response&#xa;⑥ AG ONE normalises → SDK renders answer / runs action / shows chips · Experion persists JSONL + audit in parallel" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=4;fontFamily=Courier New;" vertex="1" parent="1">
